you derailed my life! Again!

790
01:13:31,599 --> 01:13:36,950
Frank, it's not personal.
It's just programming.

791
01:13:38,387 --> 01:13:40,203
We're here!

792
01:13:46,893 --> 01:13:47,990
Where are you going?

793
01:13:48,015 --> 01:13:50,995
This is where your wire
station's located, isn't it?

794
01:13:51,020 --> 01:13:52,638
We need to get to
the Spectacle.

795
01:13:52,663 --> 01:13:55,283
- Spectacle?
- Hey. Are you insane?

796
01:13:55,308 --> 01:13:57,709
They know that you sent her to me,
they're gonna be waiting for us.

797
01:13:57,734 --> 01:14:00,590
Fine. Give me the Edison tube
and we'll go without you.

798
01:14:00,615 --> 01:14:02,576
I don't have the
Edison tube.

799
01:14:02,568 --> 01:14:04,473
It's in your bag.

800
01:14:04,620 --> 01:14:06,453
I have X-ray vision.

801
01:14:06,478 --> 01:14:09,189
- When did you get X-ray vision?
- Oh. She's full of surprises.

802
01:14:09,214 --> 01:14:12,372
I know all about her surprises.
Chief among them is this,

803
01:14:12,397 --> 01:14:14,597
she doesn't care about you.

804
01:14:14,622 --> 01:14:18,717
All that charm and the sense of
purpose and the cute little smile.

805
01:14:18,742 --> 01:14:20,282
It's all just software.

806
01:14:20,307 --> 01:14:23,351
It's 1s and 0s.
That's it.

807
01:14:23,672 --> 01:14:27,128
Trust me, when you get
there, you're on your own.

808
01:14:28,019 --> 01:14:29,858
What happened to you two?

809
01:14:29,883 --> 01:14:31,160
He thinks
I hurt him.

810
01:14:31,185 --> 01:14:35,466
No. You hurt a dumb kid that
was stupid enough to fall...

811
01:14:40,019 --> 01:14:42,874
You were many things,
Frank Walker.

812
01:14:44,952 --> 01:14:47,335
But you were
never dumb.

813
01:14:52,100 --> 01:14:53,802
Why don't you just
give me the Edison tube?

814
01:14:53,827 --> 01:14:55,592
- I'm not giving you anything.
- And...

815
01:14:55,619 --> 01:14:56,859
I'm...!

816
01:15:02,244 --> 01:15:03,689
Alright.

817
01:15:03,714 --> 01:15:07,955
You want in? I'll
bring you in. Why not.

818
01:15:07,980 --> 01:15:12,356
What's better than waiting around here and
getting hunted and killed, etc, etc.

819
01:15:12,381 --> 01:15:14,141
- That's the spirit!
- Et cetera?

820
01:15:14,166 --> 01:15:16,516
What's the et cetera?

821
01:15:39,799 --> 01:15:41,340
What kind of cables are these?

822
01:15:41,365 --> 01:15:43,102
The kind that transmit people.

823
01:15:43,127 --> 01:15:46,507
People, like us?
What, like a miniature teleport...

824
01:15:46,532 --> 01:15:48,145
Do I have to
explain everything?

825
01:15:48,170 --> 01:15:51,698
Can't you just be
amazed and move on?

826
01:15:51,723 --> 01:15:54,811
This is all wired to
the dish up there.

827
01:15:57,688 --> 01:16:00,772
Are you-
Are you using satellite?

828
01:16:02,220 --> 01:16:04,320
I know how things work.

829
01:16:04,672 --> 01:16:07,050
Well, zip-a-Dee-doo for you.

830
01:16:08,199 --> 01:16:10,160
Wrap this around your eyes, tight.

831
01:16:10,161 --> 01:16:13,848
- Why?
- Because justice is blind.

832
01:16:14,680 --> 01:16:17,393
Just.
Do it, kid.

833
01:16:17,703 --> 01:16:21,278
You want me to put
this over my head?

834
