1014
01:33:10,369 --> 01:33:11,826
Pick one.

1015
01:33:13,780 --> 01:33:17,252
Canaveral,
Cape Canaveral.

1016
01:33:31,509 --> 01:33:32,867
Easy.

1017
01:33:32,926 --> 01:33:37,421
The Interface is oriented from
your hands to the center of the Earth.

1018
01:33:37,447 --> 01:33:39,692
Okay, I got it.

1019
01:33:44,825 --> 01:33:46,987
You've trained her, obviously.

1020
01:33:47,012 --> 01:33:49,110
I just met her yesterday.

1021
01:33:49,599 --> 01:33:51,533
She knows how things work.

1022
01:33:59,185 --> 01:34:00,522
How is this possible?

1023
01:34:00,547 --> 01:34:03,515
We are millions of
exponential deviances

